<HEAD>Children Withdrawn from Program After Nude Photos Viewed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHARLESTON, W.Va. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Three parents withdrew their children
from a day-care program after the children saw nude photographs at a
